# Supabase credentials for the PWA. Copy to `web/.env` and fill in real values.
# The anon key is public-safe (RLS-protected) — it's meant to ship to the browser.
# If these are missing the app still runs; sign-in is simply disabled.
#
# Point local development at the DEV Supabase project (boardhang-dev), NOT prod.
# Production creds live only in Vercel's env vars — never in this file (it's gitignored
# but for deploys Vercel injects its own env anyway). See CONTEXT.md → "Two Supabase
# projects — dev vs prod".
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-dev-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-dev-anon-key
